icity<br><br>The numbers changed are in the attribute base columns. Most of them in attribute 3 and most getting a negative number Jedah line getting a negative 32 for attribute 3 and Naki line getting a negative 13 in attribute 3. I can't really see the differance for the Gallenite line, but EQcaster shows it as being different from what it was before the patch.<br><br>Anyone have some caster friends seeing a change?<br><br>This is not intended to foster any kind of paranoia. I myself have no idea what the changes do. <br><br>Edit. Found one change I'm pretty sure of in the naki line (spell casting haste) there have been 2 attributes added. Attribute 4 is 4000 and attribute 5 is 9500, I think it means casting time for spells it will effect. Meaning only spells with cast times between 4 seconds and 9.5 seconds. Just a guess<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ustbb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>St BB</A> at: 3/21/02 6:33:13 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umanr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Manr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 6:52:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10400.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Some focus item effects changed with 3/21 patch</span><hr size=1> And those in power keep their stronghold... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugrimmlokk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimmlokk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://grimmlokk.homestead.com/files/icon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 7:12:45 am)</font><br>   <