35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10400.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What was changed</span><hr size=1> [QUOTE] I think there SHOULD BE FOCUS ITEMS IN GAME, but only from drops off of uber mobs or have the effects of the summoned items reduced. Everyone knows casters need the help to get their damage efficiency up, but its lame to just hand it out with summoned items. [/QOUTE] <br><br>Its just another thing for Newbies to beg high level casters for...along with KEI from enchanters... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubethene.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bethene</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 8:13:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10400.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Some focus item effects changed with 3/21 patch</span><hr size=1> The items have/had two purposes.<br><br>To increase the attractiveness of mages to groups.<br><br>To increase the power of casters.<br><br>This is why they were summoned, IMHO. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzzod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zzod</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/21/02 8:21:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=10400.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Some focus item effects changed with 3/21 patch</span><hr size=1> ...And they both still do that...